{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC03_LIN_610.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x34,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Linca, after we get through this forest, what do you say we stop for a snack?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I second that. Ayesha, your snacks bring me the biggest pleasure when I am doing my duty... Ayesha!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yes? If you're worried about the snacks, I brought a lot. Your favorite‐ "
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Get behind me!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x233,
            "name_id": 0x55,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Frrr!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Kyah...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Tyah!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Th-Thank you so much... You saved me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Linca, your swordsmanship is always amazing...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I only have total confidence in handling a sword. I will not be defeated by some wild beast."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "However...maybe it is not enough to only have a sword..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "(Huh? She got depressed all of a sudden... I wonder if something's wrong...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Umm, did something happen?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Marion gave me another mission, but I do not believe I can achieve it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I am a useless person after all..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "(She was working so hard to make friends, so what could be causing so much trouble for her...?)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Is it that difficult of a mission? What is it exactly?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "She told me to...find out exactly what I want to do, and it can't be just sword fighting."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "(Hmm, that sounds a little different from a mission...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Marion always tells me to do absurd things. I wonder if she dislikes me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Umm, I think Marion is thinking about you a lot."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Is that so? I only have my sword and myself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I think it is impossible for me to find something other than that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I don't know what Marion's real intentions are, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I don't think she's saying that swords are bad. Instead, maybe it's to think of how to use your sword..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Is what I think this might be about..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "How to use my sword...? Well, there are various ways, like cutting, striking, slicing, and smashing..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Well, umm, that's not what I meant. I think it's more about what you want to do with your sword."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Like become famous, or fight your way to the top, or defeat a strong enemy... Something like that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Defeat a strong enemy! I see...<CR>I think I may be able to do that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "The problem now is to find a strong enemy... Ayesha, do you know of any?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Linca, why do you only want to do the last one? Wouldn't becoming famous be okay, too?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x12,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "The other two have elements that make them difficult to understand."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "But defeating a strong enemy is easy to understand, so I thought that one was good."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "Well, the important thing here is to find out what you want to do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "Do you think that you want to do that with all your heart?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "That...hrgggh."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x168,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "What do I want to do?<CR>I wonder... Hmmm..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x16a,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x16b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, that is a very hard question. I do not think I can find the answer right away, even if I think really hard."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "So for now, what if I defeat a strong enemy and then think about it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, if you say so, I think that'll be okay..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x79,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, a strong enemy might have already arrived. Ayesha! Step back!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x233,
            "name_id": 0x55,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Pi!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "msg_string": "Th-This is..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x7c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2d,
            "msg_string": "Yes, it is a bit lacking to be considered a strong enemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x233,
            "name_id": 0x55,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2e,
            "msg_string": "Piii!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2f,
            "msg_string": "Then let's do this. When I think of a strong enemy that'll suit you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x30,
            "msg_string": "I'll come let you know right away.<CR>Does that sound okay?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x31,
            "msg_string": "Please do! I will continue to wait for you to report!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x32,
            "msg_string": "(To find something you want to do... It does sound really hard...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x33,
            "msg_string": "(Even I'd have trouble if I was told to find something I want do, other than making medicine.)"
        }
    ]
}